column5: Happy Bday Norm hope you got to enjoy this great weather

Hey Steve...I'm getting old enough to receive two pensions (76)...  No blackflies yet or skeeters...  Big Cliff and your fat little buddy (CPH) are terrorizing Sturgeon Lake while Meely and Buckster, Zen and I wetted our lines in Lake X...  I go by the saying..."if Tony ain't catchin' any, They're not in yet"...just like the carp in Peterpatch...'nuff said...
Happy Birthday Beans.
Happy Belated Birthday Norm!  Hope you had a great day!
Hey Norm, Happy Birthday to you, hope it's a great day and the fishing gods are kind to you...  Maureen
It's your birthday AGAIN Norm? Didn't you just have one of those? Have a great day my friend.
Happy B-Day Norm and all the best to you Bud !!
Have a great day my friend
Tip of the hat to you Norm.
~~~How many Bdays do you get in a year, HAPPY BIRTHDAY YOU OLDER PHART
Good Morning and HAPPY BIRTHDAY Beans.......and THANK YOU for that fish recipe.....it was VERY GOOD.  Bob
Happy BDay!
Happy Birthday Beansie. I hope you have a great day
Have a great day Beans.
Happy Birthday Norm!
Happy birthday Beans !!! All the best to you my friend
Happy birthday Norm and many returns.
THIS IS YOUR BIRTHDAY CARD, (IT'S ALSO YOUR PRESENT!) Have a great day!
Happy Birthday Norm!!   Hope you have a super day hon.  Joey
Happy B-day Beans
AGAIN?????????? LOL  Happy birthday bud.
It's a great thing you're still having these Birthdays Norm!!! Otherwise..  Enjoy your day!!
Have yourself a great one
Happy Birthday Norm.  Yep, you're among those of us who seem to have a birthday coming up every 3 or 4 months.  We should be getting the hang of it any time now.
Happy birthday beans!! Enjoy this beautiful day bud!! Hopefully, your out fishing, and hammering on some crappies for dinner  S.
Seems like this happens every year!! Happy Bday!
Happy Birthday Norm hope you have a great day.  Art

'Nudder birthday? You should be ALMOST old enough to get your pension now, eh? Are you, Meeley & Big Cliff gonna go after a few of those cute l'il fishies today?  Do they still come into beautiful Lake 'X' around this time? Just curious . . . .   any sign's of black flies yet?  P. S.  Lew . . . .   are you going to stand by when Beansie fires up those candles?
Thanks for all the swell wishes guys and gals...Y'All are terrific...  And honest injun...I only have but one a year...
